<h1 style="margin: 0 0 24px 0; font-size: 28px; font-weight: 800; color: #1a1a1a; line-height: 1.2;">Reset your password</h1>
<p style="margin: 0 0 16px 0; font-size: 16px; color: #374151; line-height: 1.6;">We received a request to reset the password for <strong><%= @user.email %></strong>.</p>
<p style="margin: 0 0 16px 0; font-size: 16px; color: #374151; line-height: 1.6;">If you did not ask for this, you can ignore this email. The link expires in 72 hours.</p>

<%= render partial: 'user_mailer/cta_button', locals: { text: 'Reset password', url: @reset_url } %>

<p style="margin: 24px 0 0 0; font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280; line-height: 1.5;">If the button does not work, copy and paste this URL into your browser:<br/><span style="word-break: break-all;"><%= @reset_url %></span></p>
